name: Buck_Wingate
text:
Buck Wingate
Buck Wingate was the wrestling coach at Twin Peaks High School.
In March 1989, Wingate observed Nadine Hurley's immense strength in the weight room and decided to try and recruit her on the wrestling team. To convince the boys on the team to accept her on the team, he told a story about a football coach who would not accept black players on his team until he witnessed a talented black halfback play. He then had her wrestle with district champion Mike Nelson.
